Appointments for two #CapeCod COVID-19 vaccination clinics opened for booking today at 9 am.

Were you able to get an appointment? How was the process? Let us know below, or email our reporter @jbarnesnews: jennette_barnes@capeandislands.org #vaccine #COVID19 #CapeandIslands https://t.co/hPQRrM7yN3
